<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Openmap</title>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="../javascripts/validation.js" defer></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="../javascripts/signup.js" defer></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/user/signup.css" />
</head>
<body>
<section class="signup-form" id="signup-form">
<div>
  <div class="title">
    <h2>운영중인 업체가 있으신가요?</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <button style="font-size:16px; width:18%; height:18%; margin-left:10px; margin-top:10%;border:none; background-color: #fff;" onclick="onSignUpTypeClick('owner')"><img src="../images/admin.png" alt="">업주 회원가입</button>
    <button style="font-size:16px; width:22%; height:22%; margin-left:230px; margin-top:20px;border:none; background-color: #fff;" onclick="onSignUpTypeClick('user')"><img src="../images/user.png" alt="">일반 회원가입</button>
  </div>
</div>
</section>

